messages.text: Are you ready yet? I wanna leave
Hold on
What? I’m waiting outside in the car
South side entrance. FYI it’s pouring so hurry up
I’m trapped
What? Trapped where?
In this freight elevator
I can’t tell if you’re joking
I’m not. I wanted to get down faster so I got in here instead of taking the stairs...
...and now it’s stuck and I can’t get the doors to open
Smart move. Real smart
Can you get in here so you can find someone to fix this and let me out of here?
I think all the janitors went home already
Would any teachers be around?
Mr. McGarvey just drove off. In his stupid Prius
OK, can you just come in yourself?
Have you tried that emergency button?
Yeah, it’s not working. None of the buttons are. I’m stuck
Great
I just wanna get out of here
Should I call 911 or something
No don’t. I don’t wanna make this into a big thing
Just get here and help me out
Fine. I’m about to miss the Patriots game so you owe me for this
Can you just shut up and come get me out of here
I get to copy your math homework until the end of the trimester
NOAH I’M SERIOUS JUST COME GET ME OUT OF HERE
Alright alright I’m coming. Hang tight
I’m soaked already just running from my car to the doors
I’m so sorry. Try being locked in a freight elevator
God this place looks so creepy when no one’s here
I bet
Maybe I should call a custodian or something
It’s fine, just get here and we can both try to open the doors together
Where is the freight elevator?
Like way way in the back, near the band rehearsal rooms
Okay
How’re you holding up in there?
Not super well. I keep hitting the buttons but nothing’s working
Well keep trying
It’s getting really claustrophobic in here
Okay I’ll be there soon
I just have this really weird feeling I’m gonna be stuck in here forever
Don’t say that. You’re not going to be
It’s just a feeling.
Did you just hear that?
That thunder? Yeah it scared the crap out of me
Noah the lights just went out
What really?
Yeah it’s pitch black
Okay well the lights just went out here in the hallways too
Are there any candles anywhere?
Candles? I’m using the light from my phone you weirdo
Sorry, not thinking straight
It’s fine
How close are you
Idk. Close
I think
OK. Hurry up, I’m starting to freak out
Okay
There’s something written here
Written where?
Like in between the buttons
What’s it say
“HELP ME”
Last person who was stuck in there probably wrote that
Probably
I hear a noise. Is that you?
No I’m not even near the band rooms yet
It’s coming from above me
What?
Like there’s someone making a noise above me. It sounds like heavy breathing
You can stop messing with me now, I’m already doing you a huge favor here
There’s someone on top of this elevator right now. It’s breathing
Tell them to shut up and help you out
I called out to it but it didn’t respond
That’s weird
Noah I’m getting scared
What do you think it is?
I have no idea. Please hurry
I’m already running soaking wet through this pitch black hallway with my phone light...
I’m not sure how much faster you want me to go
It’s getting louder
Noah?
Yeah?
Something’s trying to get in here. It doesn’t sound human
Wtf
Crap I just tripped. Screen just cracked
The elevator’s shaking
What?
It’s like rocking and forth
I’ll be there soon just stay calm
I don’t understand what’s happening
Just stay calm Larissa it’ll be fine
Oh god it’s getting so much louder. It’s trying to get inside
What is it??
I don’t know but I’m so scared Noah
Stay calm
My phone’s dying
Should I call 911 now?
It’s about to get inside oh my God. There’s nothing I can do
I’m by the band rooms I’ll be right there Larissa
It’s inside
Do you hear me Larissa? I’m outside yelling
Larissa?
LARISSA
Larissa can you hear me? Are you alright?
Why aren’t you responding? I can’t find the freight elevator
LARISSA!!
I’m here. I’m fine
What?
I’m okay
Why did you scare me like that? What was all that?
It was nothing. Please just get me out of here
Where is the freight elevator?
Do you see that mural on the wall? The one of the old man?
Yeah I’m passing by it right now
Larissa what just happened? What was the voice?
You walk past it and then take a left and you’ll see the elevator
Okay
You better have a good explanation for all this
I see it
Good. I’ll help you open it
Okay about to open it now
Where are you? I’m inside but I don’t see you anywhere at all
Larissa?
The doors just closed on me
What is this?
I’m so sorry Noah
What’s going on? Where are you?
I can’t open the doors. I’m stuck in here
Larissa?
Larissa? Answer me. Larissa?
LARISSA!
